{"talk":{"id":2882,"name":"Karoliina Korppoo: How a video game might help us build better cities","description":"With more than half of the world population living in cities, one thing is undeniable: we are an urban species. Part game, part urban planning sketching tool, \"Cities: Skylines\" encourages people to use their creativity and self-expression to rethink the cities of tomorrow. Designer Karoliina Korppoo takes us on a tour through some extraordinary places users have created, from futuristic fantasy cities to remarkably realistic landscapes. What does your dream city look like?","slug":"karoliina_korppoo_how_a_video_game_might_help_us_build_better_cities","recorded_at":"2017-04-24 00:00:00","published_at":"2017-09-22 15:00:22","updated_at":"2021-04-09 19:43:39","viewed_count":1426417,"emailed_count":0,"event":{"id":455,"name":"TED2017"},"images":[{"image":{"size":"113x85","url":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/7e7e76feaf7a2ea33745acc6f9a93e0c218fcc91_113x85.jpg"}},{"image":{"size":"240x180","url":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/7e7e76feaf7a2ea33745acc6f9a93e0c218fcc91_240x180.jpg"}},{"image":{"size":"615x461","url":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/7e7e76feaf7a2ea33745acc6f9a93e0c218fcc91_615x461.jpg"}},{"image":{"size":"2400x1800","url":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/7e7e76feaf7a2ea33745acc6f9a93e0c218fcc91_2400x1800.jpg"}}],"image_16x9":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/0c5594cd994976144a87c7c58d14f504c9719219_2880x1620.jpg","media":{"internal":{"64k":{"uri":"https:\/\/download.ted.com\/talks\/KaroliinaKorppoo_2017-64k.mp4?apikey=c692baa7dafbf74e4fbde1ac88b44cafc96cfe7a","filesize_bytes":4286386,"mime_type":"video\/mp4"},"180k":{"uri":"https:\/\/download.ted.com\/talks\/KaroliinaKorppoo_2017-180k.mp4?apikey=c692baa7dafbf74e4fbde1ac88b44cafc96cfe7a","filesize_bytes":11835661,"mime_type":"video\/mp4"},"320k":{"uri":"https:\/\/download.ted.com\/talks\/KaroliinaKorppoo_2017-320k.mp4?apikey=c692baa7dafbf74e4fbde1ac88b44cafc96cfe7